1
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:20,200
Dalang.

2
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,240
Dalang.

3
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,800
She betrayed you first

4
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,000
and caused you to suffer like this.

5
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,960
It's all because of her.

6
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,800
I am the Paper Doll Goddess.

7
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,360
I came here today

8
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,959
to guide you

9
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:07,300
through this romantic tribulation.

10
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,400
Bullshit Paper Doll Goddess!

11
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,530
I think you clearly harmed my husband.

12
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,000
The seven-year itch

13
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,840
causes couples to drift apart.

14
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,640
That woman

15
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,840
was formed by the itch bugs on your body.

16
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:20,720
And this is all because your heart was stirred by lust.

17
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,360
Nonsense!

18
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,920
I have always been devoted to my husband.

19
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,980
Dare you say that towards Wang Shiqi,

20
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:28,680
you never had the slightest romantic thought?

21
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:34,320
I only treat him as a younger brother.

22
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,800
To break this,

23
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:38,240
you must cast away all distracting thoughts.

24
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:40,800
Besides being a virtuous wife to your husband,

25
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:43,240
you must show your sincerity with a blood sacrifice

26
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,960
to dispel the itch bugs,

27
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:47,560
keeping both of you safe

28
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,970
and allowing you to grow old together.

29
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,000
Blood sacrifice?

30
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,440
The seven-year itch.

31
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,840
Couples drift apart.

32
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:57,170
All dreams arise from the mind.

33
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,840
See for yourself.

34
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,120
Itch bug.

35
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:08,919
What's wrong with me?

36
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,280
Why did I think of Shiqi?

37
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,480
Is this what is in my heart?

38
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:17,720
No.

39
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,600
Brother Shiqi.

40
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,210
So it was a dream.

41
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,560
Only by using your blood as a sacrifice,

42
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,160
placed on the table at midnight,

43
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:56,840
until the itch bugs are completely cleared,

44
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,360
can the curse be broken.

45
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:19,800
Madam,

46
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,940
be careful not to catch a cold.

47
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,010
Could Wang Shiqi really be the source?

48
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,170
Don't worry.

49
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,720
From now on,

50
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:32,960
I won't ask about anything regarding you.

51
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,720
Until you finish

52
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,640
the affairs in Taohua Town and return to the camp,

53
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,920
I won't see him again

54
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,000
or mention him.

55
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,560
Okay.

56
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,240
Song Ping has used the Warlord's power

57
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,040
to completely control the town.

58
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,440
If we don't think of a way,

59
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,090
everyone will be in danger.

60
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,320
Why haven't I seen Miss Feng?

61
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,930
Could something have happened to her too?

62
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,200
That person,

63
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,000
seeing the situation turning bad,

64
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,600
slipped away faster than a mouse.

65
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:05,460
Who knows where she ran off to now.

66
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,600
Oh, right.

67
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,640
And that warlord,

68
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,440
is like a puppet.

69
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,680
That Madam too,

70
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,840
saying something about

71
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,170
surviving a love trial.

72
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,240
What does that even mean?

73
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,500
Looking at it this way,

74
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,600
could it be

75
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,760
that Song Ping really used some dark magic

76
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,090
to control the warlord?

77
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,320
No.

78
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:27,340
Besides looking a bit tired and haggard,

79
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,660
like he overindulged,

80
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,680
I don't see any problem.

81
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:32,810
To think that

82
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:35,050
even Brother Wang can't see anything.

83
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,140
I just remembered something.

84
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,720
There was a previous mayor.

85
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,490
They were originally a loving couple.

86
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,880
But suddenly one day,

87
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,800
his temperament changed drastically.

88
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,730
He insisted on taking a concubine,

89
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,760
which caused them to fall out.

90
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,930
What happened to the couple later?

91
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:56,280
On the day of the wedding,

92
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,200
they killed each other.

93
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:01,200
In the end, both died in the town hall.

94
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:04,220
According to the people who buried them,

95
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,360
the way they died

96
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,760
was absolutely miserable and terrifying.

97
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,960
It seemed like their blood was drained.

98
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,680
What are you doing?

99
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,440
In the middle of the night?

100
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,480
We've been married for so long.

101
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,340
Why are you acting so mysterious?

102
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:19,800
Madam,

103
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:23,280
since you said you want to be with me forever,

104
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,120
I will give you

105
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,200
a big gift today.

106
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:42,600
Madam,

107
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,440
it's my wedding day.

108
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,860
Shouldn't you give me a wedding gift?

109
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,360
My husband,

110
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,159
let's drain her blood today

111
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,960
as a wedding gift for the two of us.

112
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,680
From now on,

113
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,159
you and I

114
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,760
will grow old together.

115
00:05:59,200 --> 00:05:59,880
Okay.

116
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,240
Okay.

117
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,600
Who are you talking to?

118
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,600
My wife, of course.

119
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,320
Didn't you hear?

120
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,520
She wants to drain your blood.

121
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,360
Go quickly.

122
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,560
Don't keep my wife waiting.

123
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,020
Don't delay our

124
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,900
wedding night.

125
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:30,560
Didn't you say you'd do anything for me?

126
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,760
How can you not even do this?

127
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,040
Do you still deserve to be a wife?

128
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,520
Look closely.

129
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,200
She's been standing there all along

130
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,400
without making a sound.

131
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,130
Impossible.

132
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,000
Absolutely impossible.

133
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,800
I see

134
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,850
you're just unwilling,

135
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,400
so you want to fool me.

136
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,720
Wife,

137
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,080
Wife.

138
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,560
Don't rush.

139
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,600
I'll drain her blood

140
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,480
and give it all to you.

141
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:12,560
Dalang,

142
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,700
what's wrong with you?

143
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,360
Wake up.

144
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,960
I'm your wife.

145
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,160
My bride is here.

146
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,160
What are you?

147
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,160
I want to see

148
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,960
what kind of monster you are

149
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,760
to bewitch my husband like this.

150
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:37,360
Have you seen my wife's beauty clearly?

151
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,720
How can you compare to her?

152
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,560
Since you are so heartless,

153
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:53,159
I have to use force.

154
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,800
Let me go.

155
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,570
Let me go.

156
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,320
Madam.

157
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,120
Song Ping,

158
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:11,440
so it was you who used Gu worms to create the illusion of the goddess

159
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,770
to bewitch the Warlord.

160
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,000
Congratulations, Warlord.

161
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,960
It really is you behind this.

162
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,490
Madam, what are you saying?

163
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,360
I'm just following the Warlord's orders.

164
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,800
I've prepared a wedding gift.

165
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,360
Dalang,

166
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,280
wake up.

167
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,340
Don't be controlled by Song Ping.

168
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,559
It's useless.

169
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,400
Once bewitched by the Paper Goddess,

170
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,960
no one can escape.

171
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,000
Besides, the Warlord

172
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,610
has long been tired of a shrew like you.

173
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,690
Who are you calling a shrew?

174
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,200
You are a shrew.

175
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,800
The warlord

176
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,960
would rather like the Paper Goddess

177
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,880
than you.

178
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,210
If you're not a shrew, what are you?

179
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,640
Quite strong, aren't you?

180
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,440
Hold her down!

181
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,760
Then I congratulate the warlord

182
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,760
on his happy marriage.

183
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,700
Wang Shiqi.

184
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,460
How did you get in here?

185
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,600
Thinking a few guns can stop me?

186
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,400
Ridiculous.

187
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,840
Kill him!

188
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,640
You are so thin.

189
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,500
It must have been hard for you.

190
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,640
Again?

191
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,400
I specialize in this.

192
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,560
My wife.

193
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,800
What is this?

194
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,840
Why are there so many bugs?

195
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,360
What is this?

196
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,640
So this is the so-called itch.

197
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,640
It's just a Gu worm

198
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,280
that makes people hallucinate.

199
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,760
This illusion is so thin.

200
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,860
It must have been hard for you.

201
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,360
Stop right there!

202
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:52,760
Madam.

203
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,560
Don't, don't.

204
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,080
You called me a shrew just now, didn't you?
